                <h4 data-uuid="e7f85c86031740f6bb7788711297648e">Main Idea</h4>
                <p class="main-idea" data-uuid="0c06580f0a2849d09b0c4ab2a06a278b">Crowded urban areas faced a variety of social problems.</p>
                <h2 data-uuid="7476bb8113244586af4594ab0970b468">Urban Problems</h2>
                <div class="yellow-star-yellow-bar" data-uuid="c0a95b6e90024c21b41bae026177b343"></div>
            </article>
        </section>
